<br>
The list is set at the very beginning by whoever gets agro. MT will normally be first, and then, whoever is 2nd to get on the agro list, will be second on the rampage list. The agro list changes constantly based on what actions they are taking. The rampage list ALWAYS remains the same.<br>
<br>
The only way to not be the rampage person is to die, or move out of range.<br>
<br>
Since you are a slower, you are getting on list because you usually slow right after MT start. If you don't want to be on rampage, you need to get a 2nd tank to get on the agro list before you cast. Can be nothing more than plinking with an arrow to set rampage.<br>
<br>
Oh, blurring the mob wil reset the rampage list completely. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=818.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=818.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=818.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=818.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.threadControl?topicID=818.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=818.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=818.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table bord